result.name: Girlboss by Master Kama

reviews.text:
22Dec18: came again and ordered another set and dishes and drinks, I ordered seafoods, the seafoods are not really good, the kids menu are not that good as well (it cost $78), the 波子汽水 like a water more than soft drink, I ordered a tea with teapot as well, but the taste of tea was really really not good. Also, waitresses did not said “WELCOME BOSS”, I don’t really concern about it actually, but I was wondering whether they have standard training for staff. 

A month ago: Nice decoration, place is clean, the arrangement is good and no need to wait a long time. Price is at middle level in Tuen Mun. Some dishes and drinks not just for photo taking but taste is good. Although not many staff, the service is responsive and they welcome all guests and say “ WELCOME BOSS”, that’s why they still have many customers to come after 8pm. My friend and I ordered “Two people set”, the potion is good for two and we are full (drinks not included in set). However, the beef is not that juicy. Overall I would happy to give B-, the bonus given was because the beautiful drinks.

在市廣場的三樓，較開揚的位置，空間較為寬敞。 粉紅色的主題，有不少的影相位。用『點心紙』點菜十分方便。 Bossy Royal Set $368 

黑松露醃漬蕃茄仔瑞士芝士玻璃杯沙律 一人一杯沙律🥗，自己動手搖匀沙律醬汁，味道酸酸的，芝士大大粒，好有份量。

 蟹肉牛油果蘋果青瓜沙律 沙律份量不多，蘋果牛油果🥑配上蟹肉，口感豐富，好清新，好開胃。

 龍蝦芝士雞翼 雞皮脆肉嫩，芝士味濃郁，半份有兩隻，份量剛好
香草白醬焗大蜆薯蓉 蜆肉鮮甜肥美，薯蓉配上芝士，口感香滑。

低溫慢煮三文魚烤露筍薯蓉香草荷蘭汁 經過低溫慢煮的三文魚，保持鮮味。好多薯蓉。意式龍蝦海鮮薄餅 即焗的薄餅，薄脆香口，有不少龍蝦肉，配上芝士、以及黑醋汁作調味，十分滋味。

海膽忌廉蟹肉意粉海膽鮮甜，不少蟹肉混在意粉內，每條意粉都掛上醬汁。

Unicorn Dream 粉紅色和粉藍色的配搭很夢幻，味道是巨峰提子加波子汽水，不會太甜。 
Yellow Bus 椰子加菠蘿是我的最愛，飲到最尾也是濃濃的鮮果味道！整體來說，份量好適合。可以試多幾款不同的菜式，啱女生之飯聚！
朋友帶我們在這裏享用午餐😋😋，試試這裏的味道很好，飲品很有特色，還有舒服的座位，這裏傾吓計飲下茶食下野都算不錯👍🏿
坐得唔舒服 位置小 開放式 冷氣唔夠 食物份量細 肉質好鞋 唔值 唔會再去
不過不失

reviews.text: Vast selection of baby related merchandise, Parents favorite. A huge supermarket sits next to this department store as well. A true one stop shop for families
Huge mall, connected to other shopping as well.  Good transportation options in and out.
Great place for shopping, especially for beauty products! Family mall with everything you need.

Central location. Linked to 5 or 6 other shopping arcades. Linked to the subway line at Tuen Mun station. Many car parks, and some offer free parking with purchase. I'm happy with this place as I'm always able to find whatever I'm looking for here. Finding my car after getting parking ticket stamped is always a challenge tho.
This is the closest to home and what you get.ftom.anywhere, you get it here  mostly, why ho anywhere else. My kids are practical, when they are here, they love it just here.
